            <img src="~/images/HtmlAgility_Logo.png" alt="HtmlAgilityPack Logo" class="logo" width="125px">
            <h3 class="service-heading-title">HtmlAgilityPack</h3>
            <p class="service-description">HtmlAgilityPack is used for parsing and extracting information from static HTML pages. It helps us analyze website structure when JavaScript rendering is not required.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 service-name" id="selenium">   
            <img src="~/images/Selenium_logo.png" alt="Selenium Logo" class="logo" width="100px">         
            <h3 class="service-heading-title">Selenium</h3>
            <p class="service-description">Selenium allows us to scrape and analyze websites with dynamic JavaScript content. It simulates browser interactions to access elements that static parsers cannot reach.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
